{"tid":685520,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果撐俄羅斯政府玩河蟹　　竟四月中起阻止Telegram更新","createTime":"2018-05-31T12:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T07:05:17.000Z","uid":35542,"like":195,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"276d7ce16fd69c1a3d3d54b021804336318645cd","tid":685520,"uid":35542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/05/telegram-update-blocked-because-of-russian-government/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F05%2Ftelegram-update-blocked-because-of-russian-government%2F&d=siiFE3nr6b4IiDtnS%2B4Vi26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=fae5b493\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/05/telegram-update-blocked-because-of-russian-government/</a><br />\n蘋果過往對美國政府企硬，贏得不少讚賞。可惜的是，近來不停配合中國政府河蟹，然後亦配合俄羅斯政府做河蟹動作。據稱，最受歡迎的加密聊天軟件之一Telegram，因拒絕交出加密鑰匙，蘋果竟然配合俄羅斯政府，全球封鎖Telegram更新。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，Telegram自四月中起，就被蘋果河蟹，無法在全球向用戶提供更新，以至最新的版本無法與iOS 11.4兼容，顯示出現不正常的情況。Telegram和不少用戶都不明白，為什麼因為Telegram在俄羅斯被禁，蘋果卻要禁止它在全球App Store的更新推出。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Telegram @durov<br />\n<br />\n對住FBI就咁強硬<br />\n對住中共俄羅斯就咁聽話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cced73e610461a870a8bf66fd5031265ac8cf2f","tid":685520,"uid":35542,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://telegram.org/faq#q-what-about-gdpr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Ffaq%23q-what-about-gdpr&d=siiFE3nr6b4IiDtnS%2B4Vi26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0c8c5d98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/faq#q-what-about-gdpr</a><br />\nWe're still working with our lawyers on an update to the Telegram Privacy Policy (although you shouldn't expect any dramatic changes there). Android users got their GDPR update in version 4.8.9. <span style=\"color: red;\">Unfortunately, Apple has been blocking Telegram from updating its iOS app globally since mid-April.</span>"},{"pid":"1a53ea43e2630f13f6f5b2232b7e17e853f63ebb","tid":685520,"uid":35135,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"i狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bccb180e15f52b1f09f6331b00510ec24d518de","tid":685520,"uid":35542,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/durov/87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdurov%2F87&d=siiFE3nr6b4IiDtnS%2B4Vi26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c994ffb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/durov/87</a><br />\nUnfortunately, some Telegram features, such as stickers, don&rsquo;t work correctly under iOS 11.4 that was just released &ndash; even though we fixed this issue weeks ago. <br />\n<br />\nApple has been preventing Telegram from updating its iOS apps globally ever since the Russian authorities ordered Apple to remove Telegram from the App Store. Russia banned Telegram on its territory in April because we refused to provide decryption keys for all our users&rsquo; communications to Russia&rsquo;s security agencies. We believe we did the only possible thing, preserving the right of our users to privacy in a troubled country. <br />\n<br />\nUnfortunately, Apple didn&rsquo;t side with us. While Russia makes up only 7% of Telegram&rsquo;s userbase, Apple is restricting updates for all Telegram users around the world since mid-April. As a result, we&rsquo;ve also been unable to fully comply with GDPR for our EU-users by the deadline of May 25, 2018. We are continuing our efforts to resolve the situation and will keep you updated.<br />\n<br />\nSorry for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience."},{"pid":"74940b3fef04c9f4a0d0529b7c56d32aea8c2eea","tid":685520,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces